 ch! Här var dagens\, sammanfattat:\n\nFull Ingebrigtsen Backe: 2x10x200m\
 n	•	Moderate hill (5–8%)\, 45–60s reps\n	•	Jog/walk back down\, 2
 –3 min between sets\n	•	Controlled threshold effort—not sprinting!\n
