DTEND;TZID=Europe/Stockholm:20151001T175210
DTSTAMP:20260328T050213Z
UID:strava-407273007@carlydergard
DESCRIPTION:Notes:\nRunning sensor study på Idrottshögskolan. Jätteför
 kyld\, detta var typ lagom träningspass. Mådde bättre efter. (8kmh for 
 3 minutes\, 10kmh for 3 minutes\, 12kmh for 3 minutes\, 15kmh for 3 minute
 s + 15kmh for 10 sec analysis)\n\nResultat :\n - Bra fotisättning\, med h
 äl först (helt ok).\n - Instable pelvis\, hip drop on both sides (hip ab
 ductors/tensor fasciae latae. Ska hålla höfterna parallella med marken)\
 n - Stable leg axis.\n - Instable ankle! Worse on right side.\n - Upper bo
 dy compensates for instable pelvis. \n - Not economical arm movement\, "to
  much abducted"\, not along body.\nRecommendations:\nStrenghten:\n - Hip a
 bductors! (Utsida höfterna\, muskeln som lyfter benet rakt åt sidan). \n
  - Strenghten core muscles (abs\, obliques\, lower back)\nStability ankle 
 joint:\n - Coordination exercise (eg standing on wobbling mats)\n - Torsio
 nal stiff running shoes with firm heel counter.\nRunning technique:\n - Ar
 m swing in running direction\, avoid rotation.\n - Arm swing close to uppe
 r body.\n\nStats:\nDistance: 2.29 km\nTime: 12:10\nAvg pace: 5:19 min/km\n
 Elevation gain: 0 m
URL:https://www.strava.com/activities/407273007
END:VEVENT
